title: [Fayhlia's Fineries, Northwest]
description: Paned windows of rose-colored glass impart a cheery glow at this corner of the shop as sunlight streams through.  Several small imperfections in the surface create thin beams of pure white light that slice across the room.
Paned windows of rose-colored glass create pale pink blocks of light on the floor.  Silhouettes of tree branches dance to their solitary rhythms, contrasting with the pale moonglow.
